text: Alin Roșu (born 21 August 1989) is a Romanian handballer who plays for Steaua București and the Romania national team. ==Achievements== *Liga Națională: **Silver Medalist: 2017, 2018 *Cupa României: **Third Place: 2017 ==Individual awards== *All-Star Left Wing of the Liga Națională: 2018 ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Botoșani Category:Romanian male handball players Category:CSA Steaua București (handball) players
